query:
INSERT INTO character (
                character_id,
                character_name,
                corporation_id,
                corporation_name,
                alliance_id,
                alliance_name
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (character_id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                corporation_id = EXCLUDED.corporation_id,
                corporation_name = EXCLUDED.corporation_name,
                alliance_id = EXCLUDED.alliance_id,
                alliance_name = EXCLUDED.alliance_name,
                updated_at = NOW()
